('3319755', '怦然心动', 'Flipped','[\'90分钟\']', '2010', '[\'美国\']', '[\'2010-07-26(好莱坞首映)\', \'2010-09-10(美国)\']', '布莱斯（卡兰•麦克奥利菲 Callan McAuliffe 饰）全家搬到小镇，邻家女孩朱丽（玛德琳•卡罗尔 Madeline Carroll 饰）前来帮忙。她对他一见钟情，心愿是获得他的吻。两人是同班同学，她一直想方设法接近他，但是他避之不及。她喜欢爬在高高的梧桐树上看风景。但因为施工，树被要被砍掉，她誓死捍卫，希望他并肩作战，但是他退缩了。她的事迹上了报纸，外公对她颇有好感，令他十分困惑。她凭借鸡下蛋的项目获得了科技展第一名，成了全场焦点，令他黯然失色。她把自家鸡蛋送给他，他听家人怀疑她家鸡蛋不卫生，便偷偷把鸡蛋丢掉。她得知真相，很伤心，两人关系跌入冰点。她跟家人诉说，引发争吵。原来父亲一直攒钱照顾傻弟弟，所以生活拮据。她理解了父母，自己动手，还得到了他外公的鼎力相助。他向她道歉，但是并未解决问题。他开始关注她。鸡蛋风波未平，家庭晚宴与午餐男孩评选又把两人扯在了一起……©豆瓣', '{\'small\': \'http://img1.doubanio.com/view/photo/s_ratio_poster/public/p501177648.jpg\', \'large\': \'http://img1.doubanio.com/view/photo/s_ratio_poster/public/p501177648.jpg\', \'medium\': \'http://img1.doubanio.com/view/photo/s_ratio_poster/public/p501177648.jpg\'}', '[\'英语\']', '[{\'avatars\': {\'small\': \'http://img3.doubanio.com/view/celebrity/s_ratio_celebrity/public/p1379484184.83.jpg\', \'large\': \'http://img3.doubanio.com/view/celebrity/s_ratio_celebrity/public/p1379484184.83.jpg\', \'medium\': \'http://img3.doubanio.com/view/celebrity/s_ratio_celebrity/public/p1379484184.83.jpg\'}, \'name_en\': \'Rob Reiner\', \'name\': \'罗伯·莱纳\', \'alt\': \'https://movie.douban.com/celebrity/1031903/\', \'id\': \'1031903\'}]', '[{\'avatars\': {\'small\': \'http://img3.doubanio.com/view/celebrity/s_ratio_celebrity/public/p16442.jpg\', \'large\': \'http://img3.doubanio.com/view/celebrity/s_ratio_celebrity/public/p16442.jpg\', \'medium\': \'http://img3.doubanio.com/view/celebrity/s_ratio_celebrity/public/p16442.jpg\'}, \'name_en\': \'Madeline Carroll\', \'name\': \'玛德琳·卡罗尔\', \'alt\': \'https://movie.douban.com/celebrity/1031867/\', \'id\': \'1031867\'}, {\'avatars\': {\'small\': \'http://img1.doubanio.com/view/celebrity/s_ratio_celebrity/public/p22277.jpg\', \'large\': \'http://img1.doubanio.com/view/celebrity/s_ratio_celebrity/public/p22277.jpg\', \'medium\': \'http://img1.doubanio.com/view/celebrity/s_ratio_celebrity/public/p22277.jpg\'}, \'name_en\': \'Callan McAuliff