('1291858', '鬼子来了', '鬼子来了','[\'139分钟\', \'162分钟(戛纳电影节)\']', '2000', '[\'中国大陆\']', '[\'2000-05-12(戛纳电影节)\', \'2002-04-27(日本)\']', '第二次世界大战期间，中国河北挂甲台村的农民马大三（姜文饰）在日本人的统治下过着平静的生活。一个晚上，游击队绑架了日军陆军士兵花屋小三郎（香川照之饰）和翻译董汉臣，把他们捆绑塞入麻袋放在马大三家里，并吩咐马好好看管，几天后的大年三十来带人。马大三和村民战战兢兢地看守两人，花屋小三郎和董汉臣数次发出求救信号，皆被村民化解。半年过去了，村民们担心事情暴露，却又不敢把花屋等放了。 马大三最终被董汉臣说动，把花屋和董送到了日军宪兵队驻地，以换取粮食。日军宪兵军官酒冢猪吉是花屋的同乡。他表面上对马等人客气，但背后指责花屋让皇军蒙耻并殴打了他。宪兵队整队去马的村子里和村民联欢送粮，酒到酣时却乍露杀机。©豆瓣', '{\'small\': \'http://img1.doubanio.com/view/photo/s_ratio_poster/public/p2553104888.jpg\', \'large\': \'http://img1.doubanio.com/view/photo/s_ratio_poster/public/p2553104888.jpg\', \'medium\': \'http://img1.doubanio.com/view/photo/s_ratio_poster/public/p2553104888.jpg\'}', '[\'汉语普通话\', \'日语\', \'唐山话\']', '[{\'avatars\': {\'small\': \'http://img9.doubanio.com/view/celebrity/s_ratio_celebrity/public/p1517818343.94.jpg\', \'large\': \'http://img9.doubanio.com/view/celebrity/s_ratio_celebrity/public/p1517818343.94.jpg\', \'medium\': \'http://img9.doubanio.com/view/celebrity/s_ratio_celebrity/public/p1517818343.94.jpg\'}, \'name_en\': \'Wen Jiang\', \'name\': \'姜文\', \'alt\': \'https://movie.douban.com/celebrity/1021999/\', \'id\': \'1021999\'}]', '[{\'avatars\': {\'small\': \'http://img9.doubanio.com/view/celebrity/s_ratio_celebrity/public/p1517818343.94.jpg\', \'large\': \'http://img9.doubanio.com/view/celebrity/s_ratio_celebrity/public/p1517818343.94.jpg\', \'medium\': \'http://img9.doubanio.com/view/celebrity/s_ratio_celebrity/public/p1517818343.94.jpg\'}, \'name_en\': \'Wen Jiang\', \'name\': \'姜文\', \'alt\': \'https://movie.douban.com/celebrity/1021999/\', \'id\': \'1021999\'}, {\'avatars\': {\'small\': \'http://img9.doubanio.com/view/celebrity/s_ratio_celebrity/public/p1379678916.04.jpg\', \'large\': \'http://img9.doubanio.com/view/celebrity/s_ratio_celebrity/public/p1379678916.04.jpg\', \'medium\': \'http://img9.doubanio.com/view/celebrity/s_ratio_celebrity/public/p1379678916.04.jpg\'}, \'name_en\': \'Teruyuki Kagawa\', \'name\': \'香川照之\