('21937452', '素媛', '소원','[\'122分钟\']', '2013', '[\'韩国\']', '[\'2013-10-02(韩国)\']', '她（李来 饰）是一个美丽平凡的小女孩，和爸爸妈妈生活在位于街角的家中。家里经营着以她的名字素媛命名的杂货店，母亲（严智媛 饰）作为老板娘日夜忙碌不得闲暇，父亲则在工厂干着繁重的工作。在那个飘雨的早上，素媛打着雨伞独自上学。在离学校近在咫尺的地方，她遭遇一个相貌猥琐、酒气冲天的大叔，由此开启了她的悲剧之旅。柔嫩的小花遭到暴风雨无情摧残，受伤的岂止枝枝叶叶，更是那迎着阳光无忧成长的心。无良媒体铺天盖地大肆渲染，作为受害者的素媛一家仿佛成了周身污秽的耻辱之人，被四周诧异好奇的目光所包围。 妈妈悲痛欲绝，几近崩溃。爸爸全力保护女儿，但受伤的小天使却拒绝爸爸的靠近。问凶之路伴随着天使的治愈旅程，美丽的女孩可会再露灿烂笑容？©豆瓣', '{\'small\': \'http://img9.doubanio.com/view/photo/s_ratio_poster/public/p2118532944.jpg\', \'large\': \'http://img9.doubanio.com/view/photo/s_ratio_poster/public/p2118532944.jpg\', \'medium\': \'http://img9.doubanio.com/view/photo/s_ratio_poster/public/p2118532944.jpg\'}', '[\'韩语\']', '[{\'avatars\': {\'small\': \'http://img1.doubanio.com/view/celebrity/s_ratio_celebrity/public/p1451911358.49.jpg\', \'large\': \'http://img1.doubanio.com/view/celebrity/s_ratio_celebrity/public/p1451911358.49.jpg\', \'medium\': \'http://img1.doubanio.com/view/celebrity/s_ratio_celebrity/public/p1451911358.49.jpg\'}, \'name_en\': \'Jun-ik Lee\', \'name\': \'李濬益\', \'alt\': \'https://movie.douban.com/celebrity/1028844/\', \'id\': \'1028844\'}]', '[{\'avatars\': {\'small\': \'http://img3.doubanio.com/view/celebrity/s_ratio_celebrity/public/p1403416347.83.jpg\', \'large\': \'http://img3.doubanio.com/view/celebrity/s_ratio_celebrity/public/p1403416347.83.jpg\', \'medium\': \'http://img3.doubanio.com/view/celebrity/s_ratio_celebrity/public/p1403416347.83.jpg\'}, \'name_en\': \'Kyung-gu Sol\', \'name\': \'薛景求\', \'alt\': \'https://movie.douban.com/celebrity/1045576/\', \'id\': \'1045576\'}, {\'avatars\': {\'small\': \'http://img3.doubanio.com/view/celebrity/s_ratio_celebrity/public/p14020.jpg\', \'large\': \'http://img3.doubanio.com/view/celebrity/s_ratio_celebrity/public/p14020.jpg\', \'medium\': \'http://img3.doubanio.com/view/celebrity/s_ratio_celebrity/public/p14020.jpg\'}, \'name_en\': \'Ji-won Uhm\', \'name\': \'严志媛\', \'alt\': \'https://movie.douban.com/celebrity/1015178/\', \'id\': \'101517