('1306029', '美丽心灵', 'A Beautiful Mind','[\'135分钟\']', '2001', '[\'美国\']', '[\'2001-12-13(加州首映)\', \'2002-01-04(美国)\']', '本片是关于20世纪伟大数学家小约翰•福布斯-纳什的人物传记片。 小约翰•福布斯-纳什（拉塞尔•克劳）在念研究生时，便发表了著名的博弈理论，该理论虽只有短短26页，却在经济、军事等领域产生了深远的影响。但就在小约翰•福布斯-纳什蜚声国际时，他的出众直觉因为精神分裂症受到困扰，然而这并没阻止他向学术上的最高层进军的步伐，在深爱他的妻子艾丽西亚（珍妮弗•康纳利）的鼓励和帮助下，他走得虽然艰缓，却始终没有停步，而最终，凭借十几年的不懈努力和顽强意志，他如愿以偿。©豆瓣', '{\'small\': \'http://img3.doubanio.com/view/photo/s_ratio_poster/public/p1665997400.jpg\', \'large\': \'http://img3.doubanio.com/view/photo/s_ratio_poster/public/p1665997400.jpg\', \'medium\': \'http://img3.doubanio.com/view/photo/s_ratio_poster/public/p1665997400.jpg\'}', '[\'英语\']', '[{\'avatars\': {\'small\': \'http://img9.doubanio.com/view/celebrity/s_ratio_celebrity/public/p1546106896.5.jpg\', \'large\': \'http://img9.doubanio.com/view/celebrity/s_ratio_celebrity/public/p1546106896.5.jpg\', \'medium\': \'http://img9.doubanio.com/view/celebrity/s_ratio_celebrity/public/p1546106896.5.jpg\'}, \'name_en\': \'Ron Howard\', \'name\': \'朗·霍华德\', \'alt\': \'https://movie.douban.com/celebrity/1031844/\', \'id\': \'1031844\'}]', '[{\'avatars\': {\'small\': \'http://img9.doubanio.com/view/celebrity/s_ratio_celebrity/public/p17524.jpg\', \'large\': \'http://img9.doubanio.com/view/celebrity/s_ratio_celebrity/public/p17524.jpg\', \'medium\': \'http://img9.doubanio.com/view/celebrity/s_ratio_celebrity/public/p17524.jpg\'}, \'name_en\': \'Russell Crowe\', \'name\': \'罗素·克劳\', \'alt\': \'https://movie.douban.com/celebrity/1016674/\', \'id\': \'1016674\'}, {\'avatars\': {\'small\': \'http://img9.doubanio.com/view/celebrity/s_ratio_celebrity/public/p1485163747.76.jpg\', \'large\': \'http://img9.doubanio.com/view/celebrity/s_ratio_celebrity/public/p1485163747.76.jpg\', \'medium\': \'http://img9.doubanio.com/view/celebrity/s_ratio_celebrity/public/p1485163747.76.jpg\'}, \'name_en\': \'Ed Harris\', \'name\': \'艾德·哈里斯\', \'alt\': \'https://movie.douban.com/celebrity/1048024/\', \'id\': \'1048024\'}, {\'avatars\': {\'small\': \'http:/