('1296736', '钢琴家', 'The Pianist','[\'150分钟\']', '2002', '[\'法国\', \'德国\', \'英国\', \'波兰\']', '[\'2002-05-24(戛纳电影节)\', \'2002-09-25(法国)\']', '史标曼（艾德里安•布洛迪 Adrien Brody 饰）是波兰一家电台的钢琴师。二战即将爆发之时，他们全家被迫被赶进华沙的犹太区。在战争的颠沛流离中，家人和亲戚最终被纳粹杀害，而标曼本人也受尽种种羞辱和折磨，他侥幸得到一位朋友的帮助，暂时有了藏身之处。战争愈加猛烈，朋友不得不抛下 他回老家寻得安全的住所养育儿女。此时史标曼恶病缠身，却还要在搜捕中逃亡。在废墟的阁楼上他遇见了一名德国军官，在军官的要求下他弹奏了钢琴曲。美妙的琴声令德国军官萌发了恻隐之心，他暗暗帮助标曼直到俄军对波兰的解放到来…… 影片根据波兰钢琴家瓦拉迪斯罗•斯皮曼(Wladyslaw Szpilman)的自传体小说《死亡城市》改编。©豆瓣', '{\'small\': \'http://img3.doubanio.com/view/photo/s_ratio_poster/public/p792376093.jpg\', \'large\': \'http://img3.doubanio.com/view/photo/s_ratio_poster/public/p792376093.jpg\', \'medium\': \'http://img3.doubanio.com/view/photo/s_ratio_poster/public/p792376093.jpg\'}', '[\'英语\', \'德语\', \'俄语\']', '[{\'avatars\': {\'small\': \'http://img3.doubanio.com/view/celebrity/s_ratio_celebrity/public/p1366303762.72.jpg\', \'large\': \'http://img3.doubanio.com/view/celebrity/s_ratio_celebrity/public/p1366303762.72.jpg\', \'medium\': \'http://img3.doubanio.com/view/celebrity/s_ratio_celebrity/public/p1366303762.72.jpg\'}, \'name_en\': \'Roman Polanski\', \'name\': \'罗曼·波兰斯基\', \'alt\': \'https://movie.douban.com/celebrity/1054420/\', \'id\': \'1054420\'}]', '[{\'avatars\': {\'small\': \'http://img9.doubanio.com/view/celebrity/s_ratio_celebrity/public/p28365.jpg\', \'large\': \'http://img9.doubanio.com/view/celebrity/s_ratio_celebrity/public/p28365.jpg\', \'medium\': \'http://img9.doubanio.com/view/celebrity/s_ratio_celebrity/public/p28365.jpg\'}, \'name_en\': \'Adrien Brody\', \'name\': \'艾德里安·布洛迪\', \'alt\': \'https://movie.douban.com/celebrity/1002665/\', \'id\': \'1002665\'}, {\'avatars\': {\'small\': \'http://img9.doubanio.com/view/celebrity/s_ratio_celebrity/public/p2375.jpg\', \'large\': \'http://img9.doubanio.com/view/celebrity/s_ratio_celebrity/public/p2375.jpg\', \'medium\': \'http://img9.doubanio.com/view/celebrity/s_ratio_celebrity/public/p2375.jpg\'}, \'name_en\': \'Thomas Kretschmann\', \'name\': \'托马斯·克莱舒曼\', \'alt\': \'ht