('3442220', '海豚湾', 'The Cove','[\'92分钟\']', '2009', '[\'美国\']', '[\'2009-07-31(美国)\']', '日本和歌山县太地，是一个景色优美的小渔村，然而这里却常年上演着惨无人道的一幕。每年，数以万计的海豚经过这片海域，他们的旅程却在太地戛然而止。渔民们将海豚驱赶到靠近岸边的一个地方，来自世界各地的海豚训练师挑选合适的对象，剩下的大批海豚则被渔民毫无理由地赶尽杀绝。这些屠杀，这些罪行，因为种种利益而被政府和相关组织所隐瞒。 理查德•贝瑞（Richard O’Barry）年轻时曾是一名海豚训练师，他所参与拍摄电影《海豚的故事》备受欢迎。但是，一头海豚的死让理查德的心灵受到强烈的震撼。从此，他致力于拯救海豚的活动。不顾当地政府和村民百般阻挠，他和他的摄影团队想方设法潜入太地的海豚屠杀场，只为将罪行公之于众，拯救人类可爱的朋友…… 本片荣获2010年第82届奥斯卡金像奖最佳纪录长片奖。©豆瓣', '{\'small\': \'http://img1.doubanio.com/view/photo/s_ratio_poster/public/p2559579779.jpg\', \'large\': \'http://img1.doubanio.com/view/photo/s_ratio_poster/public/p2559579779.jpg\', \'medium\': \'http://img1.doubanio.com/view/photo/s_ratio_poster/public/p2559579779.jpg\'}', '[\'英语\', \'日语\']', '[{\'avatars\': {\'small\': \'http://img9.doubanio.com/view/celebrity/s_ratio_celebrity/public/p1354247528.95.jpg\', \'large\': \'http://img9.doubanio.com/view/celebrity/s_ratio_celebrity/public/p1354247528.95.jpg\', \'medium\': \'http://img9.doubanio.com/view/celebrity/s_ratio_celebrity/public/p1354247528.95.jpg\'}, \'name_en\': \'Louie Psihoyos\', \'name\': \'路易·西霍尤斯\', \'alt\': \'https://movie.douban.com/celebrity/1324808/\', \'id\': \'1324808\'}]', '[{\'avatars\': None, \'name_en\': \'\', \'name\': "Richard O\'Barry", \'alt\': None, \'id\': None}, {\'avatars\': {\'small\': \'http://img9.doubanio.com/view/celebrity/s_ratio_celebrity/public/p1354247528.95.jpg\', \'large\': \'http://img9.doubanio.com/view/celebrity/s_ratio_celebrity/public/p1354247528.95.jpg\', \'medium\': \'http://img9.doubanio.com/view/celebrity/s_ratio_celebrity/public/p1354247528.95.jpg\'}, \'name_en\': \'Louie Psihoyos\', \'name\': \'路易·西霍尤斯\', \'alt\': \'https://movie.douban.com/celebrity/1324808/\', \'id\': \'1324808\'}, {\'avatars\': None, \'name_en\': \'\', \'name\': \'Hardy Jones\', \'alt\': None, \'id\': None}, {\'avatars\': None, \'name_en\': \'\', \'name\': \'Michael Illiff\', \'alt\': None, \'id\': None}]'),
('1303021', '小鞋子', 'بچههای آسمان','[\'89分钟\']', '1997', '[\'伊朗\']', '[\'1997-02(伊朗)\', \'1999-01-22(美国)\']', '家境贫寒的男孩Ali（Amir Farrokh Hashemian）帮妹妹Zahra（Bahare Seddiqi）取修补好的鞋子时，不慎将鞋子弄丢，为了不被父（Mohammad Amir Naji）、母（Fereshte Sarabandi ）责罚，他央求Zahra暂时保密，说两人可以替换着穿他的鞋子上学，并答应一定会帮她买双新鞋子。 Ali原本指望用他和父亲进城打工挣的钱帮Zahra买双新鞋，父亲的意外受伤打消了他的美梦。看到全市长跑比赛季军的奖品是一双运动鞋时，Ali决定参加比赛，但是他错过了报名日期。几经哀求，老师（Dariush Mokhtari ）破例让实力出众的Ali参加了比赛。比赛场上，Ali不断提醒自己，一定要得第三名！©豆瓣', '{\'small\': \'http://img9.doubanio.com/view/photo/s_ratio_poster/public/p2173580536.jpg\', \'large\': \'http://img9.doubanio.com/view/photo/s_ratio_poster/public/p2173580536.jpg\', \'medium\': \'http://img9.doubanio.com/view/photo/s_ratio_poster/public/p2173580536.jpg\'}', '[\'波斯语\']', '[{\'avatars\': {\'small\': \'http://img3.doubanio.com/view/celebrity/s_ratio_celebrity/public/p11312.jpg\', \'large\': \'http://img3.doubanio.com/view/celebrity/s_ratio_celebrity/public/p11312.jpg\', \'medium\': \'http://img3.doubanio.com/view/celebrity/s_ratio_celebrity/public/p11312.jpg\'}, \'name_en\': \'Majid Majidi\', \'name\': \'马基德·马基迪\', \'alt\': \'https://movie.douban.com/celebrity/1275039/\', \'id\': \'1275039\'}]', '[{\'avatars\': {\'small\': \'http://img9.doubanio.com/view/celebrity/s_ratio_celebrity/public/pZqvenMj2VOEcel_avatar_uploaded1373251165.44.jpg\', \'large\': \'http://img9.doubanio.com/view/celebrity/s_ratio_celebrity/public/pZqvenMj2VOEcel_avatar_uploaded1373251165.44.jpg\', \'medium\': \'http://img9.doubanio.com/view/celebrity/s_ratio_celebrity/public/pZqvenMj2VOEcel_avatar_uploaded1373251165.44.jpg\'}, \'name_en\': \'Amir Farrokh Hashemian\', \'name\': \'法拉赫阿米尔·哈什米安\', \'alt\': \'https://movie.douban.com/celebrity/1331041/\', \'id\': \'1331041\'}, {\'avatars\': {\'small\': \'http://img1.doubanio.com/view/celebrity/s_ratio_celebrity/public/p1372182839.67.jpg\', \'large\': \'http://img1.doubanio.com/view/celebrity/s_ratio_celebrity/public/p1372182839.67.jpg\', \'medium\': \'http://img1.doubanio.com/view/celebrity/s_ratio_celebrit