('1292343', '蝴蝶效应', 'The Butterfly Effect','[\'113分钟\', \'120分钟(导演剪辑版)\']', '2004', '[\'美国\', \'加拿大\']', '[\'2004-01-23(美国)\']', '伊万（艾什顿·库奇 Ashton Kutcher 饰）曾经有一个糟糕的童年，因为他行为闯下了大祸，令他童年充满不堪回忆的往事。而事实上，他确实只是依稀记得一点可怕的情景，这些情景一直纠缠着他的正常生活。伊万接受心理学家建议，把琐碎生活记在记事本里，却偶然发现通过记事本回到过去。 这时他才清楚记起，童年时候的自己做了那么多的错事。他幻想着用现在的意识，潜入童年的身体，去弥补种种过失给人们带来的伤害，尤其是希望与当年暗恋的凯西最终走回一起。然而他一次次的跨越时空的更改，只能越来越招致现实世界的不可救药。一切就像蝴蝶效应般，牵一发而动全身。©豆瓣', '{\'small\': \'http://img1.doubanio.com/view/photo/s_ratio_poster/public/p2209066019.jpg\', \'large\': \'http://img1.doubanio.com/view/photo/s_ratio_poster/public/p2209066019.jpg\', \'medium\': \'http://img1.doubanio.com/view/photo/s_ratio_poster/public/p2209066019.jpg\'}', '[\'英语\']', '[{\'avatars\': {\'small\': \'http://img9.doubanio.com/view/celebrity/s_ratio_celebrity/public/p1563681345.26.jpg\', \'large\': \'http://img9.doubanio.com/view/celebrity/s_ratio_celebrity/public/p1563681345.26.jpg\', \'medium\': \'http://img9.doubanio.com/view/celebrity/s_ratio_celebrity/public/p1563681345.26.jpg\'}, \'name_en\': \'Eric Bress\', \'name\': \'埃里克·布雷斯\', \'alt\': \'https://movie.douban.com/celebrity/1279265/\', \'id\': \'1279265\'}, {\'avatars\': {\'small\': \'http://img3.doubanio.com/view/celebrity/s_ratio_celebrity/public/p1481012767.62.jpg\', \'large\': \'http://img3.doubanio.com/view/celebrity/s_ratio_celebrity/public/p1481012767.62.jpg\', \'medium\': \'http://img3.doubanio.com/view/celebrity/s_ratio_celebrity/public/p1481012767.62.jpg\'}, \'name_en\': \'J. Mackye Gruber\', \'name\': \'J·麦基·格鲁伯\', \'alt\': \'https://movie.douban.com/celebrity/1285555/\', \'id\': \'1285555\'}]', '[{\'avatars\': {\'small\': \'http://img1.doubanio.com/view/celebrity/s_ratio_celebrity/public/p49829.jpg\', \'large\': \'http://img1.doubanio.com/view/celebrity/s_ratio_celebrity/public/p49829.jpg\', \'medium\': \'http://img1.doubanio.com/view/celebrity/s_ratio_celebrity/public/p49829.jpg\'}, \'name_en\': \'Ashton Kutcher\', \'name\': \'阿什顿·库彻\', \'alt\': \'https://movie.douban.com/celebrity/10