('1292215', '天使爱美丽', 'Le fabuleux destin d\'Amélie Poulain','[\'122分钟\']', '2001', '[\'法国\', \'德国\']', '[\'2001-04-25(法国)\', \'2001-08-16(德国)\']', '艾米莉（奥黛丽·塔图 Audrey Tautou 饰）有着别人看来不幸的童年——父亲给她做健康检查时，发现她心跳过快，便断定她患上心脏病，从此艾米莉与学校绝缘。随后因为一桩意外，母亲在她眼前突然死去。这一切都毫不影响艾米莉对生活的豁达乐观。 1997年，戴安娜王妃的去世让她倍感人生的孤独脆弱，艾米莉从此开始了一系列助人计划，包括自闭忧郁的邻居老人，被老板刻薄的菜摊伙计、遗失了童年器物的旧房东、爱情失意的咖啡店同事。但她万万想不到，成人录象带商店店员尼诺（马修·卡索维 Mathieu Kassovitz 饰），竟成为她的棘手对象，艾米莉开始了令人哭笑不得的另类计划……©豆瓣', '{\'small\': \'http://img3.doubanio.com/view/photo/s_ratio_poster/public/p2447590313.jpg\', \'large\': \'http://img3.doubanio.com/view/photo/s_ratio_poster/public/p2447590313.jpg\', \'medium\': \'http://img3.doubanio.com/view/photo/s_ratio_poster/public/p2447590313.jpg\'}', '[\'法语\', \'俄语\']', '[{\'avatars\': {\'small\': \'http://img1.doubanio.com/view/celebrity/s_ratio_celebrity/public/p9069.jpg\', \'large\': \'http://img1.doubanio.com/view/celebrity/s_ratio_celebrity/public/p9069.jpg\', \'medium\': \'http://img1.doubanio.com/view/celebrity/s_ratio_celebrity/public/p9069.jpg\'}, \'name_en\': \'Jean-Pierre Jeunet\', \'name\': \'让-皮埃尔·热内\', \'alt\': \'https://movie.douban.com/celebrity/1054518/\', \'id\': \'1054518\'}]', '[{\'avatars\': {\'small\': \'http://img3.doubanio.com/view/celebrity/s_ratio_celebrity/public/p1973.jpg\', \'large\': \'http://img3.doubanio.com/view/celebrity/s_ratio_celebrity/public/p1973.jpg\', \'medium\': \'http://img3.doubanio.com/view/celebrity/s_ratio_celebrity/public/p1973.jpg\'}, \'name_en\': \'Audrey Tautou\', \'name\': \'奥黛丽·塔图\', \'alt\': \'https://movie.douban.com/celebrity/1004860/\', \'id\': \'1004860\'}, {\'avatars\': {\'small\': \'http://img1.doubanio.com/view/celebrity/s_ratio_celebrity/public/p34948.jpg\', \'large\': \'http://img1.doubanio.com/view/celebrity/s_ratio_celebrity/public/p34948.jpg\', \'medium\': \'http://img1.doubanio.com/view/celebrity/s_ratio_celebrity/public/p34948.jpg\'}, \'name_en\': \'Mathieu Kassovitz\', \'name\': \'马修·卡索维茨\', \'alt\': \'https://movie.douban.com/celebrity/102273