('1300299', '杀人回忆', '살인의 추억','[\'132分钟\']', '2003', '[\'韩国\']', '[\'2003-05-02(韩国)\']', '1986年，韩国京畿道华城郡，热得发昏的夏天，在田野边发现一具女尸，早已发臭。小镇警察朴探员（宋康昊饰）和汉城来的苏探员（金相庆饰）接手案件，唯一可证实的是这具女尸生前被强奸过。线索的严重缺乏让毫无经验的朴探员和搭档曹探员（金罗河饰）只凭粗暴逼供和第六感推断，几次将犯罪 嫌疑人屈打成招。而苏探员客观冷静，据理分析，几次排除嫌疑，警察内部为了证明与推翻矛盾不断，然而无辜女子还是接二连三被残忍杀害，他们只好达成共识一起合作。此时，一个极其符合作案特征的小青年（朴海日饰）成为最大嫌疑人，警方神经绷紧地锁定住他，同时DNA检测报告也被送往美国，然而案件并未在此处停止。©豆瓣', '{\'small\': \'http://img1.doubanio.com/view/photo/s_ratio_poster/public/p2326071698.jpg\', \'large\': \'http://img1.doubanio.com/view/photo/s_ratio_poster/public/p2326071698.jpg\', \'medium\': \'http://img1.doubanio.com/view/photo/s_ratio_poster/public/p2326071698.jpg\'}', '[\'韩语\', \'英语\']', '[{\'avatars\': {\'small\': \'http://img9.doubanio.com/view/celebrity/s_ratio_celebrity/public/p1388466418.95.jpg\', \'large\': \'http://img9.doubanio.com/view/celebrity/s_ratio_celebrity/public/p1388466418.95.jpg\', \'medium\': \'http://img9.doubanio.com/view/celebrity/s_ratio_celebrity/public/p1388466418.95.jpg\'}, \'name_en\': \'Joon-ho Bong\', \'name\': \'奉俊昊\', \'alt\': \'https://movie.douban.com/celebrity/1062919/\', \'id\': \'1062919\'}]', '[{\'avatars\': {\'small\': \'http://img9.doubanio.com/view/celebrity/s_ratio_celebrity/public/p345.jpg\', \'large\': \'http://img9.doubanio.com/view/celebrity/s_ratio_celebrity/public/p345.jpg\', \'medium\': \'http://img9.doubanio.com/view/celebrity/s_ratio_celebrity/public/p345.jpg\'}, \'name_en\': \'Kang-ho Song\', \'name\': \'宋康昊\', \'alt\': \'https://movie.douban.com/celebrity/1031238/\', \'id\': \'1031238\'}, {\'avatars\': {\'small\': \'http://img9.doubanio.com/view/celebrity/s_ratio_celebrity/public/p2966.jpg\', \'large\': \'http://img9.doubanio.com/view/celebrity/s_ratio_celebrity/public/p2966.jpg\', \'medium\': \'http://img9.doubanio.com/view/celebrity/s_ratio_celebrity/public/p2966.jpg\'}, \'name_en\': \'Sang-kyung Kim\', \'name\': \'金相庆\', \'alt\': \'https://movie.douban.com/celebrity/1019425/\', \'id\': \'1019425\'}, {\'avatars\': {\'small\': \'http://