('6985810', '狩猎', 'Jagten','[\'115分钟\']', '2012', '[\'丹麦\', \'瑞典\']', '[\'2012-05-20(戛纳电影节)\', \'2013-01-10(丹麦)\']', '刚刚和妻子离婚的卢卡斯（麦斯·米科尔森 Mads Mikkelsen 饰）目前在一家托儿所工作，心地善良个性温和的他很快就受到了同事和孩子们的喜爱，其中，一个名叫卡拉（安妮卡·韦德科普 Annika Wedderkopp 饰）的早熟女孩对卢卡斯尤为的亲近。面对女孩幼稚 而单纯的示好，卢卡斯只能婉转的拒绝，可令他没有想到的是，这一举动将他的生活推向了风口浪尖。 卡拉报复性的谎言让卢卡斯背负起了性侵女童的罪名，一时间，这个好好先生成为了整个小镇排挤和压迫的对象。好友的愤怒，前妻的不信任，爱犬的死亡和陌生人的恶意让卢卡斯几近崩溃，而当小小的卡拉吐露真相之后，恶意却并没有随着卢卡斯的重获清白而划下句点。©豆瓣', '{\'small\': \'http://img1.doubanio.com/view/photo/s_ratio_poster/public/p1546987967.jpg\', \'large\': \'http://img1.doubanio.com/view/photo/s_ratio_poster/public/p1546987967.jpg\', \'medium\': \'http://img1.doubanio.com/view/photo/s_ratio_poster/public/p1546987967.jpg\'}', '[\'丹麦语\', \'英语\', \'波兰语\']', '[{\'avatars\': {\'small\': \'http://img3.doubanio.com/view/celebrity/s_ratio_celebrity/public/p50973.jpg\', \'large\': \'http://img3.doubanio.com/view/celebrity/s_ratio_celebrity/public/p50973.jpg\', \'medium\': \'http://img3.doubanio.com/view/celebrity/s_ratio_celebrity/public/p50973.jpg\'}, \'name_en\': \'Thomas Vinterberg\', \'name\': \'托马斯·温特伯格\', \'alt\': \'https://movie.douban.com/celebrity/1045236/\', \'id\': \'1045236\'}]', '[{\'avatars\': {\'small\': \'http://img3.doubanio.com/view/celebrity/s_ratio_celebrity/public/p57893.jpg\', \'large\': \'http://img3.doubanio.com/view/celebrity/s_ratio_celebrity/public/p57893.jpg\', \'medium\': \'http://img3.doubanio.com/view/celebrity/s_ratio_celebrity/public/p57893.jpg\'}, \'name_en\': \'Mads Mikkelsen\', \'name\': \'麦斯·米科尔森\', \'alt\': \'https://movie.douban.com/celebrity/1040529/\', \'id\': \'1040529\'}, {\'avatars\': {\'small\': \'http://img9.doubanio.com/view/celebrity/s_ratio_celebrity/public/p48344.jpg\', \'large\': \'http://img9.doubanio.com/view/celebrity/s_ratio_celebrity/public/p48344.jpg\', \'medium\': \'http://img9.doubanio.com/view/celebrity/s_ratio_celebrity/public/p48344.jpg\'}, \'name_en\': \'Thomas Bo Larsen\', \'name\': \'托玛斯·博·拉森\', \'alt\': \'https://movie.douban.com/celebrity/1037