('2149806', '入殓师', 'おくりびと','[\'130 分钟\']', '2008', '[\'日本\']', '[\'2008-09-13(日本)\']', '买了昂贵的大提琴，想要成就一番事业的小林大悟（本木雅弘 饰），经历了4个月的管弦乐演奏，得到的却是“乐团解散”的噩耗与购买乐器的高昂债务。迫不得已，大悟与妻子美香（广末凉子 饰）搬到老屋，过着清贫的日子。某日，一则广告吸引了大悟的注意：NK代理公司，帮助旅行，高薪短工时。大悟来到NK代理公司面试，社长佐佐木生荣（山崎努 饰）二话不说就决定聘用大悟，但却对工作内容避而不谈。在大悟的再三追问下，佐佐木社长终于道明：是入殓（日语Nou Kan）工作！ 虽然心理上有所忌惮，高额的薪水还是令大悟接受了这份工作。但这样的工作对普通人谈何容易，一方面对遗体的不适，一方面又要对妻友隐瞒自己的工作，小林大悟不平凡的工作就这样开始了。©豆瓣', '{\'small\': \'http://img1.doubanio.com/view/photo/s_ratio_poster/public/p594972928.jpg\', \'large\': \'http://img1.doubanio.com/view/photo/s_ratio_poster/public/p594972928.jpg\', \'medium\': \'http://img1.doubanio.com/view/photo/s_ratio_poster/public/p594972928.jpg\'}', '[\'日语\']', '[{\'avatars\': {\'small\': \'http://img1.doubanio.com/view/celebrity/s_ratio_celebrity/public/p8539.jpg\', \'large\': \'http://img1.doubanio.com/view/celebrity/s_ratio_celebrity/public/p8539.jpg\', \'medium\': \'http://img1.doubanio.com/view/celebrity/s_ratio_celebrity/public/p8539.jpg\'}, \'name_en\': \'Yôjirô Takita\', \'name\': \'泷田洋二郎\', \'alt\': \'https://movie.douban.com/celebrity/1158861/\', \'id\': \'1158861\'}]', '[{\'avatars\': {\'small\': \'http://img9.doubanio.com/view/celebrity/s_ratio_celebrity/public/p18584.jpg\', \'large\': \'http://img9.doubanio.com/view/celebrity/s_ratio_celebrity/public/p18584.jpg\', \'medium\': \'http://img9.doubanio.com/view/celebrity/s_ratio_celebrity/public/p18584.jpg\'}, \'name_en\': \'Masahiro Motoki\', \'name\': \'本木雅弘\', \'alt\': \'https://movie.douban.com/celebrity/1036923/\', \'id\': \'1036923\'}, {\'avatars\': {\'small\': \'http://img1.doubanio.com/view/celebrity/s_ratio_celebrity/public/p50678.jpg\', \'large\': \'http://img1.doubanio.com/view/celebrity/s_ratio_celebrity/public/p50678.jpg\', \'medium\': \'http://img1.doubanio.com/view/celebrity/s_ratio_celebrity/public/p50678.jpg\'}, \'name_en\': \'Ryoko Hirosue\', \'name\': \'广末凉子\', \'alt\': \'https://movie.douban.com/celebrity/1098533/\', \'id\': \'1098533\'}, {\'avatars\': {\'small\': \'ht