('1294240', '教父3', 'The Godfather: Part III','[\'170分钟\']', '1990', '[\'美国\']', '[\'1990-12-25(美国)\']', '转眼间已经是1979年，第二代教父麦克•柯里昂（阿尔•帕西诺 饰）到了垂暮之年，为了灵魂的救赎，麦克慢慢结束家族的黑道事业，转投正当生意。 麦克的儿子托尼酷爱艺术，无意接手家族事业，迈克尔决定让大哥逊尼的私生子，火爆好色的文森（安迪•加西亚 饰）继承家业，当第三代教父。麦克的爱女玛丽（索菲娅•科波拉 饰）和文森相恋，遭到父亲的反对，父女渐渐疏远。 为了使家族资产合法化，麦克通过在梵蒂冈教廷的关系网，准备投资“屹立”集团，却遭到敌人的暗中阻挠，教皇的去世也让事情更加扑朔迷离。 麦克无奈之下，只能重新选择用暴力解决问题，他的亲人也被卷入了这场血雨腥风。©豆瓣', '{\'small\': \'http://img3.doubanio.com/view/photo/s_ratio_poster/public/p2169664351.jpg\', \'large\': \'http://img3.doubanio.com/view/photo/s_ratio_poster/public/p2169664351.jpg\', \'medium\': \'http://img3.doubanio.com/view/photo/s_ratio_poster/public/p2169664351.jpg\'}', '[\'英语\', \'意大利语\', \'德语\', \'拉丁语\']', '[{\'avatars\': {\'small\': \'http://img3.doubanio.com/view/celebrity/s_ratio_celebrity/public/p592.jpg\', \'large\': \'http://img3.doubanio.com/view/celebrity/s_ratio_celebrity/public/p592.jpg\', \'medium\': \'http://img3.doubanio.com/view/celebrity/s_ratio_celebrity/public/p592.jpg\'}, \'name_en\': \'Francis Ford Coppola\', \'name\': \'弗朗西斯·福特·科波拉\', \'alt\': \'https://movie.douban.com/celebrity/1054419/\', \'id\': \'1054419\'}]', '[{\'avatars\': {\'small\': \'http://img9.doubanio.com/view/celebrity/s_ratio_celebrity/public/p645.jpg\', \'large\': \'http://img9.doubanio.com/view/celebrity/s_ratio_celebrity/public/p645.jpg\', \'medium\': \'http://img9.doubanio.com/view/celebrity/s_ratio_celebrity/public/p645.jpg\'}, \'name_en\': \'Al Pacino\', \'name\': \'阿尔·帕西诺\', \'alt\': \'https://movie.douban.com/celebrity/1054451/\', \'id\': \'1054451\'}, {\'avatars\': {\'small\': \'http://img3.doubanio.com/view/celebrity/s_ratio_celebrity/public/p31540.jpg\', \'large\': \'http://img3.doubanio.com/view/celebrity/s_ratio_celebrity/public/p31540.jpg\', \'medium\': \'http://img3.doubanio.com/view/celebrity/s_ratio_celebrity/public/p31540.jpg\'}, \'name_en\': \'Diane Keaton\', \'name\': \'黛安·基顿\', \'alt\': \'https://movie.douban.com/celebrity/1053568/\', \'id\': \'1053568\'}, {\'avatars\': {\'