('1417598', '电锯惊魂', 'Saw','[\'103分钟\']', '2004', '[\'美国\']', '[\'2004-01-19(圣丹斯电影节)\', \'2004-10-29(美国)\']', '一觉醒来的亚当（雷•沃纳尔 Leigh Whannell饰）发现自己被困在一个废弃的厕所里。他的对面是同样命运的劳伦斯（加利•艾尔维斯 Cary Elwes 饰）——他们被人用铁链绑住了腿，并吃惊发现二人中间横亘着一个恐怖的死人。死人鲜血淋漓，左手拿录放机右手拿枪。 亚当兜里被人放进来一盘磁带，他赶紧放到录放机里。磁带里说，罗伦斯必须在今晚6点前杀死亚当，否则二人将同归于尽，劳伦斯的家人也不能幸免。而面前死人流出来的血，剧毒无比。 一个血腥的死亡游戏开始了。在剩下不多的时间里，他们必须找到线索，逃出地狱。在最后关头，当他们以为重见天日的时候，新一轮的噩梦才刚刚开始。©豆瓣', '{\'small\': \'http://img9.doubanio.com/view/photo/s_ratio_poster/public/p2565332644.jpg\', \'large\': \'http://img9.doubanio.com/view/photo/s_ratio_poster/public/p2565332644.jpg\', \'medium\': \'http://img9.doubanio.com/view/photo/s_ratio_poster/public/p2565332644.jpg\'}', '[\'英语\']', '[{\'avatars\': {\'small\': \'http://img1.doubanio.com/view/celebrity/s_ratio_celebrity/public/p1509950363.8.jpg\', \'large\': \'http://img1.doubanio.com/view/celebrity/s_ratio_celebrity/public/p1509950363.8.jpg\', \'medium\': \'http://img1.doubanio.com/view/celebrity/s_ratio_celebrity/public/p1509950363.8.jpg\'}, \'name_en\': \'James Wan\', \'name\': \'温子仁\', \'alt\': \'https://movie.douban.com/celebrity/1032122/\', \'id\': \'1032122\'}]', '[{\'avatars\': {\'small\': \'http://img9.doubanio.com/view/celebrity/s_ratio_celebrity/public/p1464358974.95.jpg\', \'large\': \'http://img9.doubanio.com/view/celebrity/s_ratio_celebrity/public/p1464358974.95.jpg\', \'medium\': \'http://img9.doubanio.com/view/celebrity/s_ratio_celebrity/public/p1464358974.95.jpg\'}, \'name_en\': \'Leigh Whannell\', \'name\': \'雷·沃纳尔\', \'alt\': \'https://movie.douban.com/celebrity/1014029/\', \'id\': \'1014029\'}, {\'avatars\': {\'small\': \'http://img1.doubanio.com/view/celebrity/s_ratio_celebrity/public/p1534498761.88.jpg\', \'large\': \'http://img1.doubanio.com/view/celebrity/s_ratio_celebrity/public/p1534498761.88.jpg\', \'medium\': \'http://img1.doubanio.com/view/celebrity/s_ratio_celebrity/public/p1534498761.88.jpg\'}, \'name_en\': \'Cary Elwes\', \'name\': \'加利·艾尔维斯\', \'alt\': \'https://movie.douban.com/celebrit