('1303037', '喜宴', '囍宴','[\'108分钟\']', '1993', '[\'中国台湾\', \'美国\']', '[\'1993-02(柏林电影节)\', \'1993-08-04(美国)\']', '伟同（赵文瑄）是事业有成的男同志，与男友赛门（Mitchell Lichtenstein）在美国过着幸福的同居日子，烦恼来自要用各种招数应对远在台北的父（郎雄）母（归亚蕾）的一次次逼婚。伟同被逼以“乖乖仔”形象修书一封声称会在美国结婚，没料父母想亲眼见证。无奈，他只得拉上来自上海的不得志的女艺术家葳葳（金素梅）“假婚”，想逃过一劫。 父母对葳葳相当满意，却对伟同的草率态度不满，为让父母满意尽快返回台北，伟同犹如“拼命三郎”使出了浑身解数。但人算不如天算，不断的波折使得父母的返台日期一次次推迟，令他和赛门的感情亮起“红灯”，而葳葳又意外怀上了他的孩子。似乎，伟同在强大的父母（传统）面前，只能选择去做一个 “表面正常”的男人。©豆瓣', '{\'small\': \'http://img9.doubanio.com/view/photo/s_ratio_poster/public/p2173713676.jpg\', \'large\': \'http://img9.doubanio.com/view/photo/s_ratio_poster/public/p2173713676.jpg\', \'medium\': \'http://img9.doubanio.com/view/photo/s_ratio_poster/public/p2173713676.jpg\'}', '[\'汉语普通话\', \'英语\']', '[{\'avatars\': {\'small\': \'http://img9.doubanio.com/view/celebrity/s_ratio_celebrity/public/p595.jpg\', \'large\': \'http://img9.doubanio.com/view/celebrity/s_ratio_celebrity/public/p595.jpg\', \'medium\': \'http://img9.doubanio.com/view/celebrity/s_ratio_celebrity/public/p595.jpg\'}, \'name_en\': \'Ang Lee\', \'name\': \'李安\', \'alt\': \'https://movie.douban.com/celebrity/1054421/\', \'id\': \'1054421\'}]', '[{\'avatars\': {\'small\': \'http://img3.doubanio.com/view/celebrity/s_ratio_celebrity/public/p13912.jpg\', \'large\': \'http://img3.doubanio.com/view/celebrity/s_ratio_celebrity/public/p13912.jpg\', \'medium\': \'http://img3.doubanio.com/view/celebrity/s_ratio_celebrity/public/p13912.jpg\'}, \'name_en\': \'Winston Chao\', \'name\': \'赵文瑄\', \'alt\': \'https://movie.douban.com/celebrity/1018759/\', \'id\': \'1018759\'}, {\'avatars\': {\'small\': \'http://img3.doubanio.com/view/celebrity/s_ratio_celebrity/public/p1433944348.33.jpg\', \'large\': \'http://img3.doubanio.com/view/celebrity/s_ratio_celebrity/public/p1433944348.33.jpg\', \'medium\': \'http://img3.doubanio.com/view/celebrity/s_ratio_celebrity/public/p1433944348.33.jpg\'}, \'name_en\': \'Sihung Lung\', \'name\': \'郎雄\', \'alt\': \'https://movie.douban.com/celebrity/1274507/\', \'id\