('1428581', '天书奇谭', '天书奇谭','[\'89分钟\']', '1983', '[\'中国大陆\']', '[\'1983(中国大陆)\']', '天庭有珍奇书籍“天书”，被锁在石龛门里三千年。看守天书的袁公对天书的内容好奇不已，他乘无人之际，偷偷拿出观看。原来，天书上记录了一百〇八条法术，袁公偷偷下凡，把天书上的内容刻在石壁上。但本意造福人类的袁公此举却触犯了天条，遭到了玉帝的惩罚。 炼丹炉里的仙丹不慎被三条狐狸偷吃了，她们变成精下凡骗人钱财，还假扮仙姑和官府勾结，欺压百姓，祸害人间。袁公便指引天赋异禀的蛋生——一个从蛋里跳出来的孩子修习天书上的法术，和狐狸精斗智斗勇，为民除害。©豆瓣', '{\'small\': \'http://img1.doubanio.com/view/photo/s_ratio_poster/public/p2515539487.jpg\', \'large\': \'http://img1.doubanio.com/view/photo/s_ratio_poster/public/p2515539487.jpg\', \'medium\': \'http://img1.doubanio.com/view/photo/s_ratio_poster/public/p2515539487.jpg\'}', '[\'汉语普通话\']', '[{\'avatars\': {\'small\': \'http://img1.doubanio.com/view/celebrity/s_ratio_celebrity/public/p37707.jpg\', \'large\': \'http://img1.doubanio.com/view/celebrity/s_ratio_celebrity/public/p37707.jpg\', \'medium\': \'http://img1.doubanio.com/view/celebrity/s_ratio_celebrity/public/p37707.jpg\'}, \'name_en\': \'Shuchen Wang\', \'name\': \'王树忱\', \'alt\': \'https://movie.douban.com/celebrity/1316862/\', \'id\': \'1316862\'}, {\'avatars\': {\'small\': \'http://img9.doubanio.com/view/celebrity/s_ratio_celebrity/public/p53764.jpg\', \'large\': \'http://img9.doubanio.com/view/celebrity/s_ratio_celebrity/public/p53764.jpg\', \'medium\': \'http://img9.doubanio.com/view/celebrity/s_ratio_celebrity/public/p53764.jpg\'}, \'name_en\': \'Yunda Qian\', \'name\': \'钱运达\', \'alt\': \'https://movie.douban.com/celebrity/1321910/\', \'id\': \'1321910\'}]', '[{\'avatars\': {\'small\': \'http://img1.doubanio.com/view/celebrity/s_ratio_celebrity/public/p53717.jpg\', \'large\': \'http://img1.doubanio.com/view/celebrity/s_ratio_celebrity/public/p53717.jpg\', \'medium\': \'http://img1.doubanio.com/view/celebrity/s_ratio_celebrity/public/p53717.jpg\'}, \'name_en\': \'Jianhua Ding\', \'name\': \'丁建华\', \'alt\': \'https://movie.douban.com/celebrity/1318218/\', \'id\': \'1318218\'}, {\'avatars\': {\'small\': \'http://img3.doubanio.com/view/celebrity/s_ratio_celebrity/public/p1566460140.52.jpg\', \'large\': \