('1959195', '忠犬八公物语', 'ハチ公物語','[\'107 分钟\']', '1987', '[\'日本\']', '[\'1987-08-01(日本)\']', '1923年，日本秋田县大馆市天降大雪，近藤家纯种秋田犬产仔，赠与县土木科长间濑。后者将其中一犬转赠东京帝国大学教授上野秀次郎（仲代达矢 Tatsuya Nakadai 饰）驯养。上野的独生女千鹤子对此欢欣鼓舞，而上野夫妇却面露难色。后来，千鹤子（石野真子 Mako Ishino饰）谈恋爱，竟怀了男友的孩子。男友专程登门造访。上野与之对谈，后者诚惶诚恐，坦言要对其女儿负责，事不宜迟，即日便举行婚礼，上野闻听此言，转怒为喜。千鹤子出嫁后，上野旋即把全部的心血与爱都投注在幼犬身上，并取名为阿八。每日上下班，阿八必在涩谷车站等候，一年四季，风雨无阻，令路人叹为观止，成为地方一道风景，主仆之情感动天地…… 本片根据真实事件改编，为1987年日本票房冠军，票房成绩高达54亿日元。©豆瓣', '{\'small\': \'http://img3.doubanio.com/view/photo/s_ratio_poster/public/p1576418852.jpg\', \'large\': \'http://img3.doubanio.com/view/photo/s_ratio_poster/public/p1576418852.jpg\', \'medium\': \'http://img3.doubanio.com/view/photo/s_ratio_poster/public/p1576418852.jpg\'}', '[\'日语\']', '[{\'avatars\': {\'small\': \'http://img1.doubanio.com/view/celebrity/s_ratio_celebrity/public/p48739.jpg\', \'large\': \'http://img1.doubanio.com/view/celebrity/s_ratio_celebrity/public/p48739.jpg\', \'medium\': \'http://img1.doubanio.com/view/celebrity/s_ratio_celebrity/public/p48739.jpg\'}, \'name_en\': \'Seijirô Kôyama\', \'name\': \'神山征二郎\', \'alt\': \'https://movie.douban.com/celebrity/1289170/\', \'id\': \'1289170\'}]', '[{\'avatars\': {\'small\': \'http://img3.doubanio.com/view/celebrity/s_ratio_celebrity/public/p39200.jpg\', \'large\': \'http://img3.doubanio.com/view/celebrity/s_ratio_celebrity/public/p39200.jpg\', \'medium\': \'http://img3.doubanio.com/view/celebrity/s_ratio_celebrity/public/p39200.jpg\'}, \'name_en\': \'Kei Yamamoto\', \'name\': \'山本圭\', \'alt\': \'https://movie.douban.com/celebrity/1012812/\', \'id\': \'1012812\'}, {\'avatars\': {\'small\': \'http://img9.doubanio.com/view/celebrity/s_ratio_celebrity/public/p33354.jpg\', \'large\': \'http://img9.doubanio.com/view/celebrity/s_ratio_celebrity/public/p33354.jpg\', \'medium\': \'http://img9.doubanio.com/view/celebrity/s_ratio_celebrity/public/p33354.jpg\'}, \'name_en\': \'Hisashi Igawa\', \'name\': \'井川比佐志\', \'alt\': \'https://movie.douban.com/celebrity/1042429/\', \'id\': \'1042429\