('4848115', '你看起来好像很好吃', 'おまえうまそうだな','[\'90分钟\']', '2010', '[\'日本\']', '[\'2010-10-16(日本)\']', '哈特（山口胜平 饰）是一只被草食性恐龙养大的霸王龙。其实，早在它破壳而出时，草食性恐龙的首领就曾命令哈特的母亲（原田知世 饰）抛弃它，但母亲却最终还是偷偷把它养大。随着年龄的增长，每天只吃野果的哈特每天饥饿难耐，最终还是抵不住本能的驱使，开始了自己食肉的残暴生涯。然而，由于母亲的影响，在哈特的内心深处，始终涌动着一颗善良的心灵。一天，偶尔遇到一只破壳而出的食草恐龙宝宝，哈特阴差阳错的被恐龙宝宝误认为是“爸爸”，而且为小恐龙取名为“很美味”，自此开始了又一段奇异的恐龙父子情。然而，伴随着生存环境的恶化，恐龙们的生存遭受着前所未有的破坏，哈特和它的亲人最终能否经得起考验…… 本篇由日本知名漫画家宫西达也的同名漫画改编，本书曾获剑渊绘本乡绘本奖大奖。©豆瓣', '{\'small\': \'http://img3.doubanio.com/view/photo/s_ratio_poster/public/p709670262.jpg\', \'large\': \'http://img3.doubanio.com/view/photo/s_ratio_poster/public/p709670262.jpg\', \'medium\': \'http://img3.doubanio.com/view/photo/s_ratio_poster/public/p709670262.jpg\'}', '[\'日语\']', '[{\'avatars\': {\'small\': \'http://img9.doubanio.com/view/celebrity/s_ratio_celebrity/public/p1547344055.84.jpg\', \'large\': \'http://img9.doubanio.com/view/celebrity/s_ratio_celebrity/public/p1547344055.84.jpg\', \'medium\': \'http://img9.doubanio.com/view/celebrity/s_ratio_celebrity/public/p1547344055.84.jpg\'}, \'name_en\': \'Masaya Fujimori\', \'name\': \'藤森雅也\', \'alt\': \'https://movie.douban.com/celebrity/1365892/\', \'id\': \'1365892\'}]', '[{\'avatars\': {\'small\': \'http://img3.doubanio.com/view/celebrity/s_ratio_celebrity/public/p1409588765.01.jpg\', \'large\': \'http://img3.doubanio.com/view/celebrity/s_ratio_celebrity/public/p1409588765.01.jpg\', \'medium\': \'http://img3.doubanio.com/view/celebrity/s_ratio_celebrity/public/p1409588765.01.jpg\'}, \'name_en\': \'Kappei Yamaguchi\', \'name\': \'山口胜平\', \'alt\': \'https://movie.douban.com/celebrity/1018954/\', \'id\': \'1018954\'}, {\'avatars\': {\'small\': \'http://img9.doubanio.com/view/celebrity/s_ratio_celebrity/public/p1516672818.15.jpg\', \'large\': \'http://img9.doubanio.com/view/celebrity/s_ratio_celebrity/public/p1516672818.15.jpg\', \'medium\': \'http://img9.doubanio.com/view/celebrity/s_ratio_celebrity/public/p1516672818.15.jpg\'}, \'name_en\': \'Rikako Aikawa\', \'name\': \'爱河里花子\', \'alt\': 