('25895901', '海街日记', '海街diary','[\'127分钟\']', '2015', '[\'日本\']', '[\'2015-05-14(戛纳电影节)\', \'2015-06-13(日本)\']', '临海古都镰仓，顺山而成的小镇，不起眼的角落里生活着香田家四姐妹。她们的父亲早年和情人离家出走，母亲则干脆将女儿们抛给了外婆照顾。外婆去世后，外孙女们继承了这栋有着悠久历史的大房子。过早担负起家庭重任的大姐香田幸（绫濑遥 饰），尽心尽力照顾着两个妹妹佳乃（长泽雅美 饰）、千佳（夏帆 饰）健康成长。这一天，父亲去世的消息传到姐妹手中。她们结伴而行参加了父亲的葬礼，并且结识了从未谋面的异母妹妹浅野铃（广濑丝丝 饰）。许是血缘中的亲近之感，幸在临行前邀请铃搬来镰仓同住。未过多久，抱着对姐姐们的憧憬，铃迈入了父亲曾经生活过的房子。四季流转，姐妹们的故事悄然上演…… 本片根据吉田秋生的同名漫画改编。©豆瓣', '{\'small\': \'http://img1.doubanio.com/view/photo/s_ratio_poster/public/p2232247487.jpg\', \'large\': \'http://img1.doubanio.com/view/photo/s_ratio_poster/public/p2232247487.jpg\', \'medium\': \'http://img1.doubanio.com/view/photo/s_ratio_poster/public/p2232247487.jpg\'}', '[\'日语\']', '[{\'avatars\': {\'small\': \'http://img1.doubanio.com/view/celebrity/s_ratio_celebrity/public/p1361354968.19.jpg\', \'large\': \'http://img1.doubanio.com/view/celebrity/s_ratio_celebrity/public/p1361354968.19.jpg\', \'medium\': \'http://img1.doubanio.com/view/celebrity/s_ratio_celebrity/public/p1361354968.19.jpg\'}, \'name_en\': \'Hirokazu Koreeda\', \'name\': \'是枝裕和\', \'alt\': \'https://movie.douban.com/celebrity/1274351/\', \'id\': \'1274351\'}]', '[{\'avatars\': {\'small\': \'http://img9.doubanio.com/view/celebrity/s_ratio_celebrity/public/p20694.jpg\', \'large\': \'http://img9.doubanio.com/view/celebrity/s_ratio_celebrity/public/p20694.jpg\', \'medium\': \'http://img9.doubanio.com/view/celebrity/s_ratio_celebrity/public/p20694.jpg\'}, \'name_en\': \'Haruka Ayase\', \'name\': \'绫濑遥\', \'alt\': \'https://movie.douban.com/celebrity/1035655/\', \'id\': \'1035655\'}, {\'avatars\': {\'small\': \'http://img9.doubanio.com/view/celebrity/s_ratio_celebrity/public/p1483767998.76.jpg\', \'large\': \'http://img9.doubanio.com/view/celebrity/s_ratio_celebrity/public/p1483767998.76.jpg\', \'medium\': \'http://img9.doubanio.com/view/celebrity/s_ratio_celebrity/public/p1483767998.76.jpg\'}, \'name_en\': \'Masami Nagasawa\', \'name\': \'长泽雅美\', \'alt\': \'https://movie.douban.com/celebrit