('3011051', '恐怖游轮', 'Triangle','[\'99 分钟\']', '2009', '[\'英国\', \'澳大利亚\']', '[\'2009-10-16(英国)\']', '单亲母亲杰西（梅利莎·乔治 饰）和一帮朋友乘游艇出海游玩，但她总有一种有不好的事情发生的感觉。不久，他们便在海上遭遇一场强烈的风暴。游艇翻船，众人落海，几经挣扎他们好不容易爬到游艇残骸上来。正当他们无计可施之时，一艘巨大的游轮向众人缓缓驶来。众人欣喜过望，未加思索便登上这艘名为“艾俄洛斯”的游轮，结果发现这竟是一艘1930年便告失踪的神秘之船，而船上更是空无一人。 随处可见的鲜血、神秘的指示以及突如其来的凶杀事件，将这群男女带入万劫不复的恐怖轮回之中……©豆瓣', '{\'small\': \'http://img9.doubanio.com/view/photo/s_ratio_poster/public/p462470694.jpg\', \'large\': \'http://img9.doubanio.com/view/photo/s_ratio_poster/public/p462470694.jpg\', \'medium\': \'http://img9.doubanio.com/view/photo/s_ratio_poster/public/p462470694.jpg\'}', '[\'英语\']', '[{\'avatars\': {\'small\': \'http://img9.doubanio.com/view/celebrity/s_ratio_celebrity/public/p51325.jpg\', \'large\': \'http://img9.doubanio.com/view/celebrity/s_ratio_celebrity/public/p51325.jpg\', \'medium\': \'http://img9.doubanio.com/view/celebrity/s_ratio_celebrity/public/p51325.jpg\'}, \'name_en\': \'Christopher Smith\', \'name\': \'克里斯托弗·史密斯\', \'alt\': \'https://movie.douban.com/celebrity/1274962/\', \'id\': \'1274962\'}]', '[{\'avatars\': {\'small\': \'http://img3.doubanio.com/view/celebrity/s_ratio_celebrity/public/p4011.jpg\', \'large\': \'http://img3.doubanio.com/view/celebrity/s_ratio_celebrity/public/p4011.jpg\', \'medium\': \'http://img3.doubanio.com/view/celebrity/s_ratio_celebrity/public/p4011.jpg\'}, \'name_en\': \'Melissa George\', \'name\': \'梅利莎·乔治\', \'alt\': \'https://movie.douban.com/celebrity/1025179/\', \'id\': \'1025179\'}, {\'avatars\': {\'small\': \'http://img9.doubanio.com/view/celebrity/s_ratio_celebrity/public/p1392878427.85.jpg\', \'large\': \'http://img9.doubanio.com/view/celebrity/s_ratio_celebrity/public/p1392878427.85.jpg\', \'medium\': \'http://img9.doubanio.com/view/celebrity/s_ratio_celebrity/public/p1392878427.85.jpg\'}, \'name_en\': \'Liam Hemsworth\', \'name\': \'利亚姆·海姆斯沃斯\', \'alt\': \'https://movie.douban.com/celebrity/1012478/\', \'id\': \'1012478\'}, {\'avatars\': {\'small\': \'http://img9.doubanio.com/view/ce