('1293460', '雨中曲', 'Singin\' in the Rain','[\'103分钟\']', '1952', '[\'美国\']', '[\'1952-04-11(美国)\']', '1927年，由唐·洛克伍德（吉恩·凯利 饰）和丽娜·雷蒙德（简·哈根 饰）主演的《皇家流氓》在好莱坞首映。由于丽娜刺耳的嗓音无法匹配其夺目的外貌，为了维护明星形象，宣传部只得安排唐一人讲话。首映后，由于钢琴师科斯莫·布朗（唐纳德·奥康纳 饰）的汽车爆胎，为了躲避疯狂的影迷，唐意外结识了能歌善舞的凯西·塞尔登（黛比·雷诺斯 饰），并被其深深吸引。数周后，首部有声电影《爵士歌手》爆红，唐与丽娜的新片《决斗骑士》不得不临时改变拍摄方式，而凯西也成为歌舞片演员。因预映口碑极差，科斯莫提议将《决斗骑士》改为歌舞片，由凯西为丽娜配音，凯西积极附议。与凯西吻别后，唐心花怒放，在雨中载歌载舞。科斯莫的计划能否奏效？幕后的凯西能否走到台前接受观众的掌声？©豆瓣', '{\'small\': \'http://img9.doubanio.com/view/photo/s_ratio_poster/public/p1612355875.jpg\', \'large\': \'http://img9.doubanio.com/view/photo/s_ratio_poster/public/p1612355875.jpg\', \'medium\': \'http://img9.doubanio.com/view/photo/s_ratio_poster/public/p1612355875.jpg\'}', '[\'英语\']', '[{\'avatars\': {\'small\': \'http://img3.doubanio.com/view/celebrity/s_ratio_celebrity/public/p19860.jpg\', \'large\': \'http://img3.doubanio.com/view/celebrity/s_ratio_celebrity/public/p19860.jpg\', \'medium\': \'http://img3.doubanio.com/view/celebrity/s_ratio_celebrity/public/p19860.jpg\'}, \'name_en\': \'Stanley Donen\', \'name\': \'斯坦利·多南\', \'alt\': \'https://movie.douban.com/celebrity/1002835/\', \'id\': \'1002835\'}, {\'avatars\': {\'small\': \'http://img9.doubanio.com/view/celebrity/s_ratio_celebrity/public/p1490085492.85.jpg\', \'large\': \'http://img9.doubanio.com/view/celebrity/s_ratio_celebrity/public/p1490085492.85.jpg\', \'medium\': \'http://img9.doubanio.com/view/celebrity/s_ratio_celebrity/public/p1490085492.85.jpg\'}, \'name_en\': \'Gene Kelly\', \'name\': \'吉恩·凯利\', \'alt\': \'https://movie.douban.com/celebrity/1049621/\', \'id\': \'1049621\'}]', '[{\'avatars\': {\'small\': \'http://img9.doubanio.com/view/celebrity/s_ratio_celebrity/public/p1490085492.85.jpg\', \'large\': \'http://img9.doubanio.com/view/celebrity/s_ratio_celebrity/public/p1490085492.85.jpg\', \'medium\': \'http://img9.doubanio.com/view/celebrity/s_ratio_celebrity/public/p1490085492.85.jpg\'}, \'name_en\': \'Gene Kelly\', \'name\': \'吉恩·凯利\', \'alt\': \'https://movie.douban.com/