('1293964', '魂断蓝桥', 'Waterloo Bridge','[\'108分钟\']', '1940', '[\'美国\']', '[\'1940-05-17(美国)\']', '第一次世界大战期间，回国度假的陆军中尉罗伊（罗伯特·泰勒）在滑铁卢桥上邂逅了舞蹈演员玛拉（费雯·丽），两人彼此倾心，爱情迅速升温。就在两人决定结婚之时，罗伊应招回营地，两人被迫分离。由于错过剧团演出，玛拉被开除，只能和好友相依为命。 不久玛拉得知罗伊阵亡的消息，几欲崩溃，备受打击。失去爱情的玛拉感到一切都失去了意义，为了生存，她和好友不得不沦为妓女。然而命运弄人，就在此时玛拉竟然再次遇到了罗伊。虽然为罗伊的生还兴奋不已，玛拉却因自己的失身陷入痛苦之中。 感到一切难以挽回的玛拉潸然离开，独自来到两人最初相遇的地点——滑铁卢桥上…©豆瓣', '{\'small\': \'http://img1.doubanio.com/view/photo/s_ratio_poster/public/p2351134499.jpg\', \'large\': \'http://img1.doubanio.com/view/photo/s_ratio_poster/public/p2351134499.jpg\', \'medium\': \'http://img1.doubanio.com/view/photo/s_ratio_poster/public/p2351134499.jpg\'}', '[\'英语\', \'法语\']', '[{\'avatars\': {\'small\': \'http://img3.doubanio.com/view/celebrity/s_ratio_celebrity/public/p16201.jpg\', \'large\': \'http://img3.doubanio.com/view/celebrity/s_ratio_celebrity/public/p16201.jpg\', \'medium\': \'http://img3.doubanio.com/view/celebrity/s_ratio_celebrity/public/p16201.jpg\'}, \'name_en\': \'Mervyn LeRoy\', \'name\': \'茂文·勒鲁瓦\', \'alt\': \'https://movie.douban.com/celebrity/1028033/\', \'id\': \'1028033\'}]', '[{\'avatars\': {\'small\': \'http://img3.doubanio.com/view/celebrity/s_ratio_celebrity/public/p3151.jpg\', \'large\': \'http://img3.doubanio.com/view/celebrity/s_ratio_celebrity/public/p3151.jpg\', \'medium\': \'http://img3.doubanio.com/view/celebrity/s_ratio_celebrity/public/p3151.jpg\'}, \'name_en\': \'Vivien Leigh\', \'name\': \'费雯·丽\', \'alt\': \'https://movie.douban.com/celebrity/1010506/\', \'id\': \'1010506\'}, {\'avatars\': {\'small\': \'http://img3.doubanio.com/view/celebrity/s_ratio_celebrity/public/p4491.jpg\', \'large\': \'http://img3.doubanio.com/view/celebrity/s_ratio_celebrity/public/p4491.jpg\', \'medium\': \'http://img3.doubanio.com/view/celebrity/s_ratio_celebrity/public/p4491.jpg\'}, \'name_en\': \'Robert Taylor\', \'name\': \'罗伯特·泰勒\', \'alt\': \'https://movie.douban.com/celebrity/1022708/\', \'id\': \'1022708\'}, {\'avatars\': {\'small\': \'http://img1.doubanio.com/view/