('1292287', '新龙门客栈', '新龍門客棧','[\'88分钟\', \'99分钟\', \'103分钟(美国)\']', '1992', '[\'中国香港\', \'中国大陆\']', '[\'1992-08-27(中国香港)\', \'2012-02-24(中国大陆)\']', '宦官专权的明朝中叶，东厂曹少钦（甄子丹）假造圣旨杀害了忠良杨宇轩，并想斩草除根杀死其后代。侠女邱莫言（林青霞）、江湖义士贺虎等人冒死救出忠良后代后，逃至边关沙漠里的龙门客栈，与杨宇轩部下周淮安（梁家辉）会合。龙门客栈实则黑店，老板娘金镶玉（张曼玉）利用乱世，以美貌和风骚 作诱饵杀人越货聚敛钱财，但她却为英俊潇洒的周淮安动了真心。为了摸清潜藏于龙门客栈中的出关暗道，周淮安将计就计，答应与金镶玉成亲。 洞房花烛夜，楼上的周淮安与金镶玉各怀心事暗中较劲，楼下的邱莫言、贺虎等人也与东厂一众“走狗”展开了明争暗斗，战事一触即发。©豆瓣', '{\'small\': \'http://img1.doubanio.com/view/photo/s_ratio_poster/public/p1421018669.jpg\', \'large\': \'http://img1.doubanio.com/view/photo/s_ratio_poster/public/p1421018669.jpg\', \'medium\': \'http://img1.doubanio.com/view/photo/s_ratio_poster/public/p1421018669.jpg\'}', '[\'汉语普通话\', \'粤语\']', '[{\'avatars\': {\'small\': \'http://img9.doubanio.com/view/celebrity/s_ratio_celebrity/public/p47134.jpg\', \'large\': \'http://img9.doubanio.com/view/celebrity/s_ratio_celebrity/public/p47134.jpg\', \'medium\': \'http://img9.doubanio.com/view/celebrity/s_ratio_celebrity/public/p47134.jpg\'}, \'name_en\': \'Raymond Lee\', \'name\': \'李惠民\', \'alt\': \'https://movie.douban.com/celebrity/1319466/\', \'id\': \'1319466\'}]', '[{\'avatars\': {\'small\': \'http://img3.doubanio.com/view/celebrity/s_ratio_celebrity/public/p793.jpg\', \'large\': \'http://img3.doubanio.com/view/celebrity/s_ratio_celebrity/public/p793.jpg\', \'medium\': \'http://img3.doubanio.com/view/celebrity/s_ratio_celebrity/public/p793.jpg\'}, \'name_en\': \'Maggie Cheung\', \'name\': \'张曼玉\', \'alt\': \'https://movie.douban.com/celebrity/1274231/\', \'id\': \'1274231\'}, {\'avatars\': {\'small\': \'http://img1.doubanio.com/view/celebrity/s_ratio_celebrity/public/p11228.jpg\', \'large\': \'http://img1.doubanio.com/view/celebrity/s_ratio_celebrity/public/p11228.jpg\', \'medium\': \'http://img1.doubanio.com/view/celebrity/s_ratio_celebrity/public/p11228.jpg\'}, \'name_en\': \'Brigitte Lin\', \'name\': \'林青霞\', \'alt\': \'https://movie.douban.com/celebrity/1044746/\', \'id\': \'1044746\'}, {\'avatars\': {\