('1760622', '香水', 'Perfume: The Story of a Murderer','[\'147分钟\']', '2006', '[\'德国\', \'法国\', \'西班牙\', \'美国\']', '[\'2006-09-07(德国)\', \'2006-09-14(法国)\', \'2006-11-24(西班牙)\', \'2007-01-05(美国)\']', '十八世纪，让-马普蒂斯特•格雷诺耶（本•韦肖 Ben Whishaw 饰）出生在巴黎最肮脏、最恶臭不堪的地方——鱼市场上。格雷诺耶天生对气味有着惊人的天赋：无论恶臭还芳香，他都一一记住，并能轻易分辨各种气味。 当他在孤儿院长到13岁的时候，被院长卖给了制皮匠。格雷诺耶在制皮铺过着犬马不如的生活。机缘巧合，格雷诺耶在香水巴尔蒂尼面前展露了其过人的天赋，进入了香水铺工作。但格雷诺耶并不仅仅满足于制作出世界上最芳香的香水，他梦想学得如何保存万物气味的方法。巴尔蒂尼告诉格雷诺耶香水的起源地在格拉斯，那里的人知道保存气味的方法。格雷诺耶拿着巴尔蒂尼的推荐信来到了格拉斯。 格雷诺耶爱上了青春少女的体香，为了把这种香味保存下来，格雷诺耶最终走上了杀手的道路。©豆瓣', '{\'small\': \'http://img9.doubanio.com/view/photo/s_ratio_poster/public/p2441127736.jpg\', \'large\': \'http://img9.doubanio.com/view/photo/s_ratio_poster/public/p2441127736.jpg\', \'medium\': \'http://img9.doubanio.com/view/photo/s_ratio_poster/public/p2441127736.jpg\'}', '[\'英语\']', '[{\'avatars\': {\'small\': \'http://img3.doubanio.com/view/celebrity/s_ratio_celebrity/public/p252.jpg\', \'large\': \'http://img3.doubanio.com/view/celebrity/s_ratio_celebrity/public/p252.jpg\', \'medium\': \'http://img3.doubanio.com/view/celebrity/s_ratio_celebrity/public/p252.jpg\'}, \'name_en\': \'Tom Tykwer\', \'name\': \'汤姆·提克威\', \'alt\': \'https://movie.douban.com/celebrity/1047989/\', \'id\': \'1047989\'}]', '[{\'avatars\': {\'small\': \'http://img1.doubanio.com/view/celebrity/s_ratio_celebrity/public/p1397997449.99.jpg\', \'large\': \'http://img1.doubanio.com/view/celebrity/s_ratio_celebrity/public/p1397997449.99.jpg\', \'medium\': \'http://img1.doubanio.com/view/celebrity/s_ratio_celebrity/public/p1397997449.99.jpg\'}, \'name_en\': \'Ben Whishaw\', \'name\': \'本·卫肖\', \'alt\': \'https://movie.douban.com/celebrity/1025149/\', \'id\': \'1025149\'}, {\'avatars\': {\'small\': \'http://img9.doubanio.com/view/celebrity/s_ratio_celebrity/public/p10644.jpg\', \'large\': \'http://img9.doubanio.com/view/celebrity/s_ratio_celebrity/public/p10644.jpg\', \'medium\': \'http://img9.doubanio.com/view/celebrity/s_ratio_celebrity/public/p10644.jpg\'}, \'name_en\': \'Ala