('1303394', '青蛇', '青蛇','[\'99分钟\']', '1993', '[\'中国香港\']', '[\'1993-11-04(中国香港)\']', '南宋是一个人妖难分的时期，法海和尚（赵文卓 饰）到处收服妖精，也扰乱了在西湖底修炼的白青二蛇。青（张曼玉 饰）曾获白（王祖贤 饰）相救，二者便以姐妹相称。姐妹俩受惑佯装成人生活在民间，白更嫁于老实书生许仙，青也同时看上了许仙，便常常以媚态勾引许仙，无奈许仙只深爱白一个。白开设了药店，以为可以自此过上安定的生活，可许仙却受不了青的百般挑逗，更发现了青白二蛇的真实身份，可他却不舍得离开家中的天姿国色。法海得知了青白二蛇的下落，更抓走了许仙。原来白为了爱情放弃修成正果，更怀有了身孕。为了救回丈夫，二蛇与法海展开了搏斗……©豆瓣', '{\'small\': \'http://img9.doubanio.com/view/photo/s_ratio_poster/public/p584021784.jpg\', \'large\': \'http://img9.doubanio.com/view/photo/s_ratio_poster/public/p584021784.jpg\', \'medium\': \'http://img9.doubanio.com/view/photo/s_ratio_poster/public/p584021784.jpg\'}', '[\'粤语\']', '[{\'avatars\': {\'small\': \'http://img1.doubanio.com/view/celebrity/s_ratio_celebrity/public/p1393840734.39.jpg\', \'large\': \'http://img1.doubanio.com/view/celebrity/s_ratio_celebrity/public/p1393840734.39.jpg\', \'medium\': \'http://img1.doubanio.com/view/celebrity/s_ratio_celebrity/public/p1393840734.39.jpg\'}, \'name_en\': \'Hark Tsui\', \'name\': \'徐克\', \'alt\': \'https://movie.douban.com/celebrity/1007152/\', \'id\': \'1007152\'}]', '[{\'avatars\': {\'small\': \'http://img3.doubanio.com/view/celebrity/s_ratio_celebrity/public/p793.jpg\', \'large\': \'http://img3.doubanio.com/view/celebrity/s_ratio_celebrity/public/p793.jpg\', \'medium\': \'http://img3.doubanio.com/view/celebrity/s_ratio_celebrity/public/p793.jpg\'}, \'name_en\': \'Maggie Cheung\', \'name\': \'张曼玉\', \'alt\': \'https://movie.douban.com/celebrity/1274231/\', \'id\': \'1274231\'}, {\'avatars\': {\'small\': \'http://img3.doubanio.com/view/celebrity/s_ratio_celebrity/public/p751.jpg\', \'large\': \'http://img3.doubanio.com/view/celebrity/s_ratio_celebrity/public/p751.jpg\', \'medium\': \'http://img3.doubanio.com/view/celebrity/s_ratio_celebrity/public/p751.jpg\'}, \'name_en\': \'Joey Wong\', \'name\': \'王祖贤\', \'alt\': \'https://movie.douban.com/celebrity/1166896/\', \'id\': \'1166896\'}, {\'avatars\': {\'small\': \'http://img1.doubanio.com/view/celebrity/s_ratio_celebri