('5964718', '一次别离', 'جدایی نادر از سیمین','[\'123分钟\']', '2011', '[\'伊朗\', \'法国\']', '[\'2011-02-15(柏林电影节)\', \'2011-03-16(伊朗)\', \'2012-11-13(中国大陆)\']', '纳德（佩曼•莫阿迪 Peyman Moadi 饰）与西敏（蕾拉•哈塔米 Leila Hatami 饰）是一对夫妻，他们的女儿叫特梅（萨日娜•法哈蒂 Sarina Farhadi 饰）。西敏希望一家三口移居国外，但是纳德坚决反对，原因是纳德的父亲患有老年痴呆症需要照顾。两人为此对薄公堂，准备离婚，但是法院驳回了她的请求。西敏赌气回了娘家。西敏走后，纳德分身乏术，聘请了一位护工瑞茨（萨瑞•巴亚特 Sareh Bayat 饰）照顾父亲。但是，父亲如厕问题始终困扰瑞茨，依《古兰经》教义，她感到禁忌重重。瑞茨的女儿陪伴在她左右，也令她分神。几个回合下来，纳德某次回家发现，父亲被绑在床上，出离愤怒的他推倒了瑞茨。没想到怀孕的瑞茨竟然流产，瑞茨丈夫怒不可遏将纳德告上了法庭，他们各执一词，然而真相却出人意料…… 本片在61届柏林电影节获金熊奖、最佳女演员和最佳男演员银熊奖。©豆瓣', '{\'small\': \'http://img9.doubanio.com/view/photo/s_ratio_poster/public/p2189835254.jpg\', \'large\': \'http://img9.doubanio.com/view/photo/s_ratio_poster/public/p2189835254.jpg\', \'medium\': \'http://img9.doubanio.com/view/photo/s_ratio_poster/public/p2189835254.jpg\'}', '[\'波斯语\']', '[{\'avatars\': {\'small\': \'http://img3.doubanio.com/view/celebrity/s_ratio_celebrity/public/p20561.jpg\', \'large\': \'http://img3.doubanio.com/view/celebrity/s_ratio_celebrity/public/p20561.jpg\', \'medium\': \'http://img3.doubanio.com/view/celebrity/s_ratio_celebrity/public/p20561.jpg\'}, \'name_en\': \'Asghar Farhadi\', \'name\': \'阿斯哈·法哈蒂\', \'alt\': \'https://movie.douban.com/celebrity/1275094/\', \'id\': \'1275094\'}]', '[{\'avatars\': {\'small\': \'http://img3.doubanio.com/view/celebrity/s_ratio_celebrity/public/p1380019202.92.jpg\', \'large\': \'http://img3.doubanio.com/view/celebrity/s_ratio_celebrity/public/p1380019202.92.jpg\', \'medium\': \'http://img3.doubanio.com/view/celebrity/s_ratio_celebrity/public/p1380019202.92.jpg\'}, \'name_en\': \'Peyman Moadi\', \'name\': \'佩曼·莫阿迪\', \'alt\': \'https://movie.douban.com/celebrity/1314289/\', \'id\': \'1314289\'}, {\'avatars\': {\'small\': \'http://img1.doubanio.com/view/celebrity/s_ratio_celebrity/public/p39937.jpg\', \'large\': \'http://img1.doubanio.com/view/celebrity/s_ratio_celebrity/public/p39937.jpg\', \'medium\': \'http://img1.doubanio.com/view/celebrity/s_ratio_celebrity/public/p399