('5908478', '我爱你', '그대를 사랑합니다','[\'118分钟\']', '2011', '[\'韩国\']', '[\'2011-02-17(韩国)\']', '飘雪的坡道上，送牛奶的老头子金万皙（李顺载 饰）邂逅了收废品的老太太宋怡芬（尹秀晶 饰）。他们的前半生各自背负着艰辛的人生：万皙年轻时我行我素，直到妻子病逝才深觉愧疚；怡芬被心爱的男人抛弃在城市角落，孩子夭折后至老未嫁。两位老人在每天凌晨寂静的街道上相遇，孤独而苦难的生活令他们渐渐靠近。在万皙孙女妍儿（宋智孝 饰）的穿针引线下，如初恋般的悸动萌发在了彼此心中。万皙的朋友、停车场管理员张军峰（宋在河 饰）一直耐心的看护着患有老年痴呆症的老伴。直到有一天，军峰得知老伴已患绝症。目睹她一次次痛苦病发，心如刀绞的军峰做出了悲伤的决定…… 影片改编自韩国著名网络漫画家姜草的同名作品，已公演的同名舞台剧亦受到好评。©豆瓣', '{\'small\': \'http://img1.doubanio.com/view/photo/s_ratio_poster/public/p1075591188.jpg\', \'large\': \'http://img1.doubanio.com/view/photo/s_ratio_poster/public/p1075591188.jpg\', \'medium\': \'http://img1.doubanio.com/view/photo/s_ratio_poster/public/p1075591188.jpg\'}', '[\'韩语\']', '[{\'avatars\': {\'small\': \'http://img1.doubanio.com/view/celebrity/s_ratio_celebrity/public/p1365588602.29.jpg\', \'large\': \'http://img1.doubanio.com/view/celebrity/s_ratio_celebrity/public/p1365588602.29.jpg\', \'medium\': \'http://img1.doubanio.com/view/celebrity/s_ratio_celebrity/public/p1365588602.29.jpg\'}, \'name_en\': \'Chang-min Choo\', \'name\': \'秋昌旼\', \'alt\': \'https://movie.douban.com/celebrity/1324596/\', \'id\': \'1324596\'}]', '[{\'avatars\': {\'small\': \'http://img3.doubanio.com/view/celebrity/s_ratio_celebrity/public/p12222.jpg\', \'large\': \'http://img3.doubanio.com/view/celebrity/s_ratio_celebrity/public/p12222.jpg\', \'medium\': \'http://img3.doubanio.com/view/celebrity/s_ratio_celebrity/public/p12222.jpg\'}, \'name_en\': \'Jae-ho Song\', \'name\': \'宋在浩\', \'alt\': \'https://movie.douban.com/celebrity/1033753/\', \'id\': \'1033753\'}, {\'avatars\': {\'small\': \'http://img1.doubanio.com/view/celebrity/s_ratio_celebrity/public/p36809.jpg\', \'large\': \'http://img1.doubanio.com/view/celebrity/s_ratio_celebrity/public/p36809.jpg\', \'medium\': \'http://img1.doubanio.com/view/celebrity/s_ratio_celebrity/public/p36809.jpg\'}, \'name_en\': \'Soon-jae Lee\', \'name\': \'李顺载\', \'alt\': \'https://movie.douban.com/celebrity/1314836/\', \'id\': \'1314836\'}, {\'avatars\